author: GameSpot
description:
Featuring Matthew Mercer, Ashley Johnson, Laura Bailey, Travis Willingham, Liam O'Brien, Marisha Ray, Taliesin Jaffe, and Sam Riegel.

To celebrate the release of the new "Mighty Nein" animated series on Prime Video, the Critical Role cast join us for a rousing game of 20 questions...with a twist. It's 24 questions, determined by a roll, in honor of Darrington Press's "Daggerheart, of 2 d12. The questions range from mostly mundane to downright wacky but with this cast? Chaos always reigns. Be sure to check out "The Mighty Nein" on Prime Video starting November 19.

#criticalrole #mightynein #themightynein
title: The Mighty Nein Cast Answers Our Most Exciting Questions | Featuring the Cast of Critical Role

author: GameSpot
description:
California Resistance is now live in Battlefield REDSEC.

The secrets of Fort Lyndon unravel as trails from The 323 lead to Ironshore Logistics and possible ties to Pax Armata.

Fight on Eastwood across all combat sizes with land vehicles and helicopters, push SABOTAGE’s protect-and-destroy objective, and hunt rare Battle Pickup stashes for the Rorsch Mk-2 SMRW railgun and MP-RMG minigun. Wield the DB-12 shotgun and M357 TRAIT revolver, then take on RODEO, a tank-driven Gauntlet mission.

#battlefield6 #bf6 #videogames #gameplay
title: Battlefield 6 - California Resistance Official Gameplay Trailer

author: GameSpot
description:
A Legend Reforged

Guild Wars Reforged | Play with No Subscription Fee

On December 3, experience Guild Wars Reforged: The award-winning online roleplaying game enjoyed by millions, now re-energized with system enhancements. From the fall of Ascalon to the desperate stand against Nightfall—every campaign is a chapter in Tyriaʼs epic history. Your adventure is just getting started!

New Features:

•Free to existing Guild Wars owners!
•New bundled low price for new players including Prophecies, Factions, and Nightfall 
•Steam Deck Verified
•Support for XInput controllers (such as the Xbox Wireless Controller)
•New quest tracking and direction system
•On-screen control guide
•UI enhanced with HD skill icons, larger text options, and quality-of-life improvements
•Support for high DPI displays
•New ambient occlusion, HD bloom, and antialiasing rendering enhancements
•Rebuilt audio system with environmental effects (no hardware support needed)

#guildwars1 #guildwarsremake #remake #videogam
title: Guild Wars Reforged - Official Announcement Trailer
